ComicInfo.Series: Grimm Fairy Tales Presents Warlord of Oz
ComicInfo.Summary:
The sequel to the best-selling Zenescope smash hit series continues! Thora's plan continues to come together as her slaves finally uncover the tomb of the arch witch Zamora. Thorne, Adraste and the Scarecrow barely survive their encounter with the Warlord while high in the mountains above the lost city Dorothy faces a new enemy who may permanently end to her second trip to Oz.
